{"tid":2137430,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都係一食辣就肚痾","createTime":"2020-08-03T02:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T03:12:15.000Z","uid":190579,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"082c75947935a54c3524cd6cc8063050c4d516db","tid":2137430,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:38:24.000Z","msg":"準時半日後就痾返出嚟<br />\n痾出嚟仲feel 到辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身體係咪仲未消化完<br />\n以前都唔係咁但呢一兩年真係次次都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a466bdcc6317f068114dd5b7e4648c35caad34c7","tid":2137430,"uid":362315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:40:24.000Z","msg":"我成日都係 食親都肚屙 但係辣嘢真係好食 🤣"},{"pid":"9a06fb4b1af19c00ad343071570b7db7bbe91b70","tid":2137430,"uid":100541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n之前都食到辣 而家食親隔日都會肚痛 痾辣屎 搞到我唔敢再食辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d428ccff7f779afc1a8d67c87f6b3fe7e2e0ee4f","tid":2137430,"uid":240374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:56:31.000Z","msg":"問過人<br />\n如果你食完辣野會痾同肚痛，證明你身體係唔適合食辣。<br />\n細佬我食左10年，痛足十年，肛都裂理，都係一樣情況"},{"pid":"0c052f9e9d9c5b8531ae60ebf097a8c5182e3a6a","tid":2137430,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"細個可以食好撚辣<br />\n<br />\n而家多少少都柯"},{"pid":"c9184776cc7028164874adad08f063113f152a76","tid":2137430,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d428ccff7f779afc1a8d67c87f6b3fe7e2e0ee4f","tid":2137430,"uid":240374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:56:31.000Z","msg":"問過人<br />\n如果你食完辣野會痾同肚痛，證明你身體係唔適合食辣。<br />\n細佬我食左10年，痛足十年，肛都裂理，都係一樣情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa5df3a75c51efdd8dc76da818b671761def929","tid":2137430,"uid":10610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"我多數食完唔係半日<br />\n一至三小時內實肚瀉<br />\n食油膩野都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2268469d92e7cc3581674eb6993077c192e2a2e","tid":2137430,"uid":247211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:05:19.000Z","msg":"以為自己出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家食辣野當清腸胃兼減肥<br />\n係有時抹屎忽抹到屎眼好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200d744b4f4d577f473f5929fac6dd0887c05c80","tid":2137430,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:06:24.000Z","msg":"要柯返啲辣屎出黎<br />\n份量少但濃度極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238e48e6353d589bff9597f282aae8faf235bc45","tid":2137430,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"我食辣 特別係雞煲一撚定屙<br />\n未必係半日<br />\n有時食完一個鐘已經勁急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72d95ed9c694a94095bfd2a8c8cb7adf007246d","tid":2137430,"uid":55390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:12:15.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲要計過 係食完6-10個鐘後就會肚痛勁急屎 個時間長短就depends on個辣度 <br />\n所以如果明知出街出成日 日頭我係唔會食辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但明明早幾年呢件事係食到接近自己極限嘅辣度先會係咁 近排就變左求其半匙羹辣油都會 但食嗰陣係接近唔覺辣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}